â€œBoss Hogg has a wonderful aroma and flavor notes. For me the euphoric effects are a bit strong but it gradually settles into a nice numbing body high which is great for my hip and back pain. â€œI tend to be a sativa girl but wanted to try this for stress relieve and lower back muscle tension. Definitely more of a body high than head high but still some cerebral effects. I will likely keep this on hand for when I am struggling with my back.â€
